data.description: Built in 2018 and showing better than new, there's so much to love about this spacious 5 bedroom, 2.5 bath home in Perry Township! Explore this home via interactive 3D home tour, complete with floor plans, video & more. Relax on the deck with pergola in the fully fenced backyard with a lovely view of the community pond, fountain, & nature area. Enjoy vinyl plank flooring throughout the main level. Kitchen features center island, breakfast bar, & stainless steel Frigidaire appliances. Plenty of room for everyone with 1 bedroom on the main and 4 upstairs. The huge primary suite boasts cathedral ceiling, double sinks, & roomy walk-in closet. Convenient upper level laundry. Garage bump out offers additional storage space & extra long driveway provides even more parking. Great location on a cul-de-sac with convenient access to nearby dining, shopping, schools, and so much more!
